OL,3,CPolice complaints not properly
OL,4,Cinvestigated, politician alleges
OL,6,FAlleged serious misconduct and
OL,7,Ffailings by Guernsey Police are not
OL,8,Fproperly investigated under a
OL,9,F"fundamentally flawed" complaints
OL,10,Fprocess, a politician has argued.
OL,12,FDeputy Rob Curgenven spoke under
OL,13,Fparliamentary privilege, which allows
OL,14,FStates Members to discuss issues in
OL,15,Fthe Chamber, and the media to report
OL,16,Fwhat is said, without the fear of
OL,17,Flegal ramifications.
