OL,3,CPolice complaints not properly
OL,4,Cinvestigated, politician alleges
OL,6,FAccording to the States of Guernsey,
OL,7,Fthe Commission is made up of local
OL,8,Fvolunteers and "supervises the most
OL,9,Fserious complaints about conduct and
OL,10,Fthose where it is in the public
OL,11,Finterest to do so", but does not
OL,12,Fconduct investigations itself.
OL,14,FGuernsey Police have not responded to
OL,15,Fthe specific incidents referenced in
OL,16,FDeputy Curgenven's speech, but tell
OL,17,FITV News that they are open to a full
OL,18,Freview of the complaints process and
OL,19,Fare keen to instil trust in the system.
