OL,3,CPolice complaints not properly
OL,4,Cinvestigated, politician alleges
OL,6,FDeputy Curgenven references the
OL,7,FCommission's 2024 annual report, which
OL,8,Fshows that 39 complaints about the
OL,9,Fconduct of police officers below the
OL,10,Frank of Superintendent were registered
OL,11,Fduring the year and it supervised 12
OL,12,Finvestigations.
OL,14,FDeputy Curgenven says the overall
OL,15,Fnumber of complaints made against
OL,16,FGuernsey Police in 2024 was 93 and
OL,17,Fadds that the Commission therefore
OL,18,Foversaw just 13% of all cases -
OL,19,Falthough this figure is disputed by
OL,20,Fthe President of Home Affairs, Deputy
OL,21,FMarc Leadbeater.
