OL,3,CPolice complaints not properly
OL,4,Cinvestigated, politician alleges
OL,6,FHe says that politicians face a choice
OL,7,Fof "tweaking a system that is
OL,8,Ffundamentally flawed, hoping patches
OL,9,Fand plasters will do. Or we can commit
OL,10,Fto building something better, from the
OL,11,Fground up".
OL,13,FThe Guernsey Police Complaints
OL,14,FCommission has not yet responded to
OL,15,FITV News's request for comment, but
OL,16,Fits annual report says it is keen to
OL,17,Ffoster "a culture of accountability
OL,18,Fand continuous learning within
OL,19,Fpolicing".
